videos.description: No. 8 Alabama's Jaden Shackelford pours in a team-high 23 points in a 70-58 victory, securing the Tide's first season sweep over Auburn since 2014.
videos.headline: Shackelford rattles in 23 to complete sweep vs. Auburn
